	<div class="fl-col-content fl-node-content"><div class="fl-module fl-module-rich-text fl-node-626430d995bbd" data-node="626430d995bbd">
	<div class="fl-module-content fl-node-content">
		<div class="fl-rich-text">
	<h4>Hi, I’m Derek Hassack. I have over  20 years professional experience helping people deal successfully with the challenges of relationship break-down and break-up.</h4>
<h4>As one client described it <em>“through working with Derek I was able to get back my confidence, think reflectively and start to move on with my life”.</em></h4>
<h4>I work with individuals or couples, usually by Zoom or telephone, sometimes face-to-face.</h4>
</div>
